                                    ዼጥሮስ፡ ብ፡ አብ፡ ወካዕበ፡ ይ፡ ኰኵሕ ፤</incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i10.5">
                                <locus from="97v" to="97v">Fols 97v–97v</locus>
                                <title>Interpretation of the Names of the 
